import React from 'react'
import { Navbar, Nav, Container } from 'react-bootstrap'

function Header() {
  return (
    <header>
      <Navbar bg="light" expand="lg" collapseOnSelect>
        <Container>
          <Navbar.Brand href="/">Charity Management System</Navbar.Brand>
          <Navbar.Toggle aria-controls="navbarScroll" />
          <Navbar.Collapse id="navbarScroll">
            <Nav className="mr-auto">
              <Nav.Link href="/discover-project">Discover Project</Nav.Link>
              <Nav.Link href="/start-a-project">Start a Project</Nav.Link>
            </Nav>
          </Navbar.Collapse>
          <Navbar.Collapse id="navbarScroll">
            <Nav className="ml-auto my-2 my-lg-0">
              <Nav.Link href="/login">Login</Nav.Link>
              <Nav.Link href="/register">Register</Nav.Link>
            </Nav>
          </Navbar.Collapse>
        </Container>
      </Navbar>
    </header>
  )
}

export default Header
